								</td>
				</tr>-->
                                <tr>
                                <td align="left" font color="#333333"> <b>ITfC</b> is a network of development professionals engaged with the discourse on Information Technology for Development.We conceptualize alternatives that blend technological possibilities with development realities.</td>
                                </tr>
                                </table>
